      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; commercial solver iterative convergence monitoring sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit numerical solver error quantification beyond iterative convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to < 1e-5 for all equations. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
