      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by senior analyst with 10+ years CFD experience in cardiovascular applications. Boundary condition inputs independently verified. Use error formal assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
