      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional and dimensionless input parameters (Reynolds number, flow coefficient) match between simulation and experiment within ±3% at all nominal validation points.",
      "rationale": "Flow coefficient (Q/ND³) and head coefficient (gH/N²D²) computed for each operating point. Experimental and CFD dimensionless parameters agree within 1.8% across all five nominal points. Reynolds numbers in the range 8,200–24,600, confirming fully turbulent regime consistent with COU nominal conditions. Equivalency confirmed at Gradation 2 for nominal operating range."
    }
